Data type specifies the type of value a variable holds. This require in programming to do various operation without causing
an error.
It is not necessary to specify the datatype in python because python is interpreted programming language that automatically
detect the variable as they define.

There are five types of data types:
1. Numeric
2. Dictionary
3. Boolean
4. Set
5. Sequence Type


Example:
a = "Apple"
print(a)

In python the data type is automatically detected as it is string type variable
